            "heading": {
                "type": "heading",
                "content": "start wp 1.2 Biedt persoonlijke verzorging, observeert en monitort gezondheid en welbevinden",
                "level": 1
            },
            "items": [
                {
                    "type": "paragraph",
                    "content": "<p><span class=\"font-size-16px\">11 dagdelen van 2 juli t/m 24 sept.</span></p>\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://www.zorgwelzijn.nl/Resizes/mainarticleimage/PageFiles/17/90/29017/001_RBIAdam-image-1362498.jpeg\" class=\"height-400-pixels width-400-pixels\"/></p>\n<p><span class=\"font-size-20px\" style=\"background-color:rgb(248, 248, 248);\">http://maken.wikiwijs.nl/62976/wp_1_2_2_juli_2015</span></p>\n"
                }
            ],
            "sections": [
                {
                    "reference": {
                        "value": "1314952"
                    },
                    "heading": {
                        "type": "heading",
                        "content": "Planning maken",
                        "level": 2
                    },
                    "items": [
                        {
                            "type": "paragraph",
                            "content": "<p><span class=\"font-size-16px\">maak een planning voor de huiswerk- en moduleopdrachten van werkproces 1.2</span></p>\n<table border=\"1\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td class=\"width-302-pixels\">\n<p><span class=\"font-size-16px\">1.Lichamelijke verzorging</span></p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"width-302-pixels\">\n<p><span class=\"font-size-16px\">Filmpje met pop maken in skillslab en verslag</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td class=\"width-302-pixels\">\n<p><span class=\"font-size-16px\">2.Observeren en monitoren van gezondheid en welbevinden</span></p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"width-302-pixels\">\n<p><span class=\"font-size-16px\">Fotocollage en verslag</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td class=\"width-302-pixels\">\n<p><span class=\"font-size-16px\">3.Ondersteunen bij eten en drinken</span></p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"width-302-pixels\">\n<p><span class=\"font-size-16px\">Fotocollage en verslag</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td class=\"width-302-pixels\">\n<p><span class=\"font-size-16px\">4.Ondersteunen bij uitscheiding</span></p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"width-302-pixels\">\n<p><span class=\"font-size-16px\">Presentatie of afdeling of in klas</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td class=\"width-302-pixels\">\n<p><span class=\"font-size-16px\">5.Ondersteunen bij mobiliteit</span></p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"width-302-pixels\">\n<p><span class=\"font-size-16px\">Informatieboekje en instructiefilmpje</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td class=\"width-302-pixels\">\n<p><span class=\"font-size-16px\">6.Slaap-waakritme bevorderen</span></p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"width-302-pixels\">\n<p><span class=\"font-size-16px\">Verslag</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td class=\"width-302-pixels\">\n<p><span class=\"font-size-16px\">7.Complicaties van immobiliteit voorkomen</span></p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"width-302-pixels\">\n<p><span class=\"font-size-16px\">Beeldverslag</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td class=\"width-302-pixels\">\n<p><span class=\"font-size-16px\">8.Voorkomen en behandelen van decubitus en smetten</span></p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"width-302-pixels\">\n<p><span class=\"font-size-16px\">Verslag</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td class=\"width-302-pixels\">\n<p><span class=\"font-size-16px\">9.Reflectieverslag</span></p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"width-302-pixels\">\n<p> </p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td class=\"width-302-pixels\">\n<p><span class=\"font-size-16px\">Moduleopdracht</span></p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"width-302-pixels\">\n<p><span class=\"font-size-16px\">Midden / hoog complexe zorgvrager 8 dagen verzorgen en verslag maken.</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n"
                        },
